md:
giải nghĩa từ "fullest" sang tiếng việt; đưa ra nghĩa tiếng việt theo từ loại và đưa ra câu ví dụ, các từ liên quan.
fullest /ˈfʊlɪst/ (adjective)
* Meaning: containing or holding as much as possible; completely full.
* Type: adjective
* Vietnamese meaning: đầy nhất, chứa được nhiều nhất.

Example sentence: The fullest container was placed at the back of the shelf.

Related words: full, fullest, fill, filling.

Note: The word "fullest" is the superlative form of the adjective "full", which means containing or holding as much as possible. It is used to describe something that is completely full or has the maximum amount of something.
